This will be a collection to remember! Capcom Fighting Collection 2 is now available on PlayStation 4!

Experience a powerful pack of iconic fighting games throughout Capcom's history, including:

Capcom vs. SNK: Millennium Fight 2000 Pro
Capcom vs. SNK 2: Mark of the Millennium 2001
Capcom Fighting Evolution
Street Fighter Alpha 3 UPPER
Project Justice
Power Stone
Power Stone 2
Plasma Sword: Nightmare of Bilstein

Featuring online play with rollback netcode, an extensive art gallery, music to groove to, and tons of quality of life updates, jump into these 8 classic titles and join the fight today!

Update 1.4 has landed! Experience the fight like never before with the new Day and Night Cycle and Dynamic Weather Systems that will push your survival tactics to the limit. Take the battle to the Bugs with the new TW-201-S Morita I, featuring an underbarrel shotgun for close-quarters devastation.
Chase side objectives with the all-new FedNet News Broadcast feature, capture heroic moments on camera, and boost your squad mates as you turn the tide against the Arachnid menace!

Starship Troopers: Extermination is available on PlayStation 5, with full cross-play!

Get ready to return to the nightmare…
The first free DLC for Ravenswatch, "Romeo & Juliet", arrives on May 27!

Rendez-vous on May 27 to play the duo inspired by the tragic tale and dive deeper into the darkness with exciting gameplay updates. Sharpen your blades, load your gun, and prepare to rewrite this story the Ravenswatch way.

🔥Two new playable heroes - Romeo & Juliet
⚔️ Choose between both characters for strategic gameplay, you can play them alone, or together to maximize their potential!

Available as a free update on PlayStation®4 and PlayStation®5 on May 27.
